snippet.title: FNAF AR Workshop Series: Toy Bonnie
snippet.description:
👀Check out Toy Bonnie in the first of the FNAF AR Workshop Series. The Workshop Series shows off just some of the great game and character art that's part of the Special Delivery game. Each video lets you check out an individual animatronic's workshop animations, a 360° view of their model, and the animatronic condition from 100%-0%.
👉 Play FNAF AR: https://t.co/CF5OrMD2R1?amp=1
🐻📦 FNAF AR Merch Store: http://merch.fnafar.com
